data.description: Beautiful Woodbridge home boasts three large bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms, large bonus room and spacious indoor laundry room. It also includes a large office downstairs. Nice size formal dining room, spacious kitchen, and family room create a comfortable and inviting living space. The kitchen is equipped with gorgeous granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample cabinet space. There's also a breakfast nook off the kitchen. The stone fireplace in the family room adds a cozy touch and makes it an ideal place to gather around during colder months.Downstairs the primary bedroom features a large walk-in closet with built-in storage and a spacious primary bathroom. Thousands in upgrades brand new hardwood flooring, tile, and a new air conditioner. Fully landscaped front and backyard with a covered patio. The property's location is a highlight, as it is within walking distance to the golf course and walking trails. Close to shopping and restaurants Low HOA dues.
